description:
Family & Friends Finder is the location-tracking app. It uses GPS location data to report the real-time whereabouts of your friends and family.  It’s an easy way to coordinate with family and friends. Simply install the Family & Friends Finder on everyone’s phone. Once registered, each member appears as an icon on the map so you’ll always know where your family members are.

Features:
* View the real-time location of friends and family members on a private map;
* Use GPS to find people who are most important for you;
* See past location history for your friends and family members;
* Invite as many people as you want to join;
* User-friendly design and easy installation.

You need to register in order to use the application.
Disclaimer: Continued usage of location services while the app is in the background can excessively drain battery.
The application is not spyware. It is intended only to coordinate the location of friends and family.
This application obliges all participants to confirm their consent to the use of their location. Each user at any time can turn off the service to determine their location.

